–[[
  This script doubles the bet after a loss but starts at a very high chance of success:  95%.&lt;br /&gt;
  After each bet the chance reduces enough to bring equilibrium to profit but stops reducing chance at 49.5%.&lt;br /&gt;
  First loss goes from 95% to 67%, then 57% and then gradually lower and closer to 49.5%.&lt;br /&gt;
